  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package embeds W-EP-02: the primary hemolysis validation result — the most narratively detailed result in the package — lacks a structured prov:wasGeneratedBy link to a generation Activity, even though the prose describes the experimental campaign and CFD post-processing steps in detail. A reviewer may incorrectly conclude that the narrative substitutes for the structured provenance reference.",
